dent.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Secret%20Service%20has%20come%20under%20intense%20scrutiny%20following%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-butler-pennsylvania-rally-secret-service-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efatal%20shooting%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20left%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20wounded%20at%20his%20rally%20Saturday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shooting%2C%20which%20killed%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-pennsylvania-rally-shooting-deaths-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erally%20attendee%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20left%20two%20others%20critically%20injured%2C%20is%20being%20investigated%20as%20an%20assassination%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shooter%20was%20killed%2C%20the%20Secret%20Service%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20news%20of%20the%20shooting%20was%20still%20breaking%2C%20notable%20figures%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewere%20quick%20to%20question%20the%20Secret%20Service%20and%20its%20leadership%20following%20the%20shooting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20investigation%20remains%20in%20its%20early%20stages%2C%20law%20enforcement%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20historic%20shooting%20will%20certainly%20prompt%20a%20major%20review%20of%20Secret%20Service%20procedure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatt%20Shoemaker%2C%20a%20former%20intelligence%20officer%20at%20the%20Defense%20Intelligence%20Agency%2C%20went%20as%20far%20as%20calling%20the%20shooting%20a%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20failure%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Secret%20Service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20to%20these%20sorts%20of%20events%20before%2C%20and%20there%20are%20layers%20upon%20layers%20of%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20Shoemaker%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20for%20the%20alleged%20shooter%20to%20be%20on%20a%20rooftop%2C%20with%20a%20clear%20shot%20to%20the%20podium%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%20mind-boggling%20to%20say%20that%20this%20was%20overlooked.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225104%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20infographic%20shows%20a%20map%20of%20the%20deadly%20shooting%20at%20a%20Trump%20rally%20in%20Pennsylvania.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669343ab5439fb59cebd3089%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223332%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20was%20hit%20in%20his%20right%20ear%20and%20is%20fine%20following%20a%20deadly%20shooting%20at%20his%20rally%20in%20Pennsylvania.%20This%20map%20shows%20how%20far%20the%20shooter%20was%20from%20Trump%20on%20stage.%3Cp%3EYasin%20Demirci%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20Truth%20Social%20several%20hours%20after%20the%206%3A15%20p.m.%20shooting%20that%20a%20bullet%20hit%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-speaks-out-after-shooting-thanks-secret-service-condolences-victim-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eupper%20part%20of%20his%20right%20ear%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20videos%20of%20the%20shooting%2C%20the%20former%20president%20could%20be%20seen%20clutching%20his%20hand%20to%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-photo-rally-shooting-republican-rallying-call-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebloodied%20face%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20later%20raising%20his%20fist%20triumphantly%20while%20being%20escorted%20off%20the%20stage%20by%20the%20Secret%20Service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Secret%20Service%20spokesperson%20directed%20Business%20Insider%20to%20public%20statements%20posted%20by%20the%20federal%20agency%20on%20social%20media%20and%20declined%20to%20answer%20specific%20questions%20about%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20Secret%20Service%20spokesperson%20Anthony%20Guglielmi%2C%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FSecretSvcSpox%2Fstatus%2F1812288378596982908%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20X%2C%20wrote%20that%20the%20suspected%20shooter%20%26quot%3Bfired%20multiple%20shots%20toward%20the%20stage%20from%20an%20elevated%20position%20outside%26quot%3B%20the%20venue%20of%20former%20President%20Trump's%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUS%20Secret%20Service%20quickly%20responded%20with%20protective%20measures%2C%20and%20the%20former%20president%20is%20safe%20and%20being%20evaluated%2C%26quot%3B%20Guglielmi's%20statement%20continued%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20FBI%20had%20been%20notified%20about%20the%20shooting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20statement%2C%20the%20FBI%20indicated%20it%20would%20be%20taking%20the%20lead%20on%20the%20investigation.%20Representatives%20for%20the%20FBI%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20briefing%20shortly%20after%20midnight%2C%20FBI%20special%20agent%20Kevin%20Rojek%20noted%20%26quot%3Bit%20is%20surprising%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20shooter%20managed%20to%20fire%20several%20rounds%20before%20being%20neutralized%20by%20the%20Secret%20Service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20the%20Secret%20Service%20were%20not%20present%20at%20the%20press%20conference%20to%20respond%20to%20questions%20about%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShoemaker%20told%20BI%20it%20appeared%20that%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20shooter%20%26quot%3Bslipped%20through%20the%20cracks%2C%26quot%3B%20despite%20firsthand%20reports%20of%20a%20witness%20who%20told%20the%20BBC%20that%20he%20saw%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feyewitness-describes-seeing-gunman-roof-during-trump-shooting-bbc-interview-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eattempted%20to%20alert%20authorities%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20man%20with%20a%20rifle%20on%20a%20roof%20nearby%20the%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20they%20didn't%20pay%20too%20much%20attention%20to%20it.%20Maybe%20they%20did%20take%20it%20seriously%2C%20but%20there%20just%20wasn't%20enough%20time%20before%20the%20shots%20rang%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Shoemaker%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20shot%20even%20happened%20%E2%80%94%20that%20the%20only%20thing%20right%20now%20that%20is%20saving%20the%20Secret%20Service%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20President%20Trump%20was%20not%20killed%2C%20which%20means%20that%20they%20were%20relying%20on%20pure%20luck%20that%20the%20individual%20that%20they're%20charged%20with%20protecting%20did%20not%20die%20%E2%80%94%20if%20they're%20relying%20on%20luck%2C%20it%20means%20that%20there%20is%20a%20problem%20and%20it%20means%20that%20there's%20a%20failure%20somewhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShoemaker%20wasn't%20alone%20in%20his%20assessment%20that%20the%20shooting%20would%20prompt%20a%20major%20examination%20of%20the%20Secret%20Service's%20policies%20and%20procedures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKen%20Gray%2C%20a%20retired%20FBI%20agent%20and%20lecturer%20in%20the%20criminal%20justice%20department%20of%20the%20University%20of%20New%20Haven%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%2C%20given%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20shooter%20was%20outside%20the%20cleared%20rally%20event%2C%20he%20expects%20future%20events%20will%20need%20to%20%26quot%3Bexpand%20the%20perimeter%20of%20the%20secured%20zone%20or%20move%20indoors.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Gray%20noted%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Btoo%20early%20to%20make%20an%20assessment%26quot%3B%20about%20whether%20the%20incident%20should%20be%20considered%20a%20complete%20security%20failure%2C%20especially%20given%20the%20flood%20of%20unconfirmed%20information%20circulating%20about%20the%20shooting%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20highest-profile%20critics%20was%20Tesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20who%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20publicly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-endorses-trump-after-pennsylvania-rally-incident-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eendorsed%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20criticized%20the%20Secret%20Service%20director%2C%20Kimberly%20Cheatle.%20Cheatle%20previously%20served%20as%20the%20head%20of%20security%20for%20the%20soft%20drink%20company%20Pepsi%20before%20leading%20the%20Secret%20Service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20before%20being%20put%20in%20charge%20of%20protecting%20the%20PRESIDENT%2C%20she%20was%20guarding%20bags%20of%20Cheetos%20%E2%80%A6%26quot%3B%20Musk%20wrote%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1812297671119638647%3Fs%3D46%26t%3D7tTelX4JT_vvwUkZXj7OXQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20X%20that%20included%20a%20screenshot%20of%20her%20biography%20and%20work%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20campaign%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Republican%20National%20Committee%2C%20have%20indicated%20the%20party's%20planned%20convention%20in%20Milwaukee%20this%20week%20will%20proceed%20following%20the%20rally%20shooting.%20It%20is%20unclear%20what%20if%20any%2C%20modifications%20will%20be%20made%20to%20the%20security%20procedures%20at%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229799b940-604a-4126-8407-076a10242638%5C%22%3EAn%20investigation%20and%20more%20visible%20security%20measures%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShoemaker%20said%20he%20expects%20to%20see%20bulletproof%20glass%20surrounding%20the%20former%20president%20in%20future%20public%20appearances%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20more%20pronounced%20use%20of%20drones%20for%20aerial%20surveillance%20at%20his%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20expect%20this%20to%20at%20least%20initial%20reports%20of%20basic%20findings%20to%20be%20released%20within%20the%20next%2048%20to%2072%20hours%2C%26quot%3B%20Shoemaker%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20they%20take%20longer%20than%20that%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20raise%20a%20lot%20of%20questions%2C%20just%20in%20terms%20of%20what%20the%20problem%20is%20%E2%80%94%20is%20the%20problem%20that%20they%20don't%20have%20enough%20expertise%20looking%20at%20this%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGOP%20House%20Speaker%20Mike%20Johnson%20vowed%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20that%20the%20House%20would%20investigate%20the%20%26quot%3Btragic%20events%26quot%3B%20that%20occurred%20at%20the%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20American%20people%20deserve%20to%20know%20the%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20have%20Secret%20Service%20Director%20Kimberly%20Cheatle%20and%20other%20appropriate%20officials%20from%20DHS%20and%20the%20FBI%20appear%20for%20a%20hearing%20before%20our%20committees%20ASAP.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20will%20lead%20an%20official%20investigation%20into%20the%20incident%2C%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20released%20Saturday%20evening.%20The%20agency%20indicated%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bclose%26quot%3B%20to%20identifying%20a%20suspect%20in%20the%20shooting%2C%20but%20a%20formal%20identification%20is%20pending%20confirmation%20through%20a%20DNA%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecret-service-scrutiny-shooting-donald-trump-pennsylvania-rally-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720935134000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669330379caa6ed01e016e48%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecret-service-scrutiny-shooting-donald-trump-pennsylvania-rally-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20Secret%20Service%20quickly%20came%20under%20scrutiny%20for%20failing%20to%20prevent%20a%20fatal%20shooting%20at%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20rally%20on%20Saturday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktangalakislippert%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecret-service-scrutiny-shooting-donald-trump-pennsylvania-rally-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Live%20Updates%3A%20Donald%20Trump%20S