ttempt%20on%20Trump%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20biggest%20opponent%20in%20the%20US%20election%20later%20this%20year%2C%20has%20set%20alarm%20bells%20ringing%20through%20the%20country's%20security%20establishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20rounds%20targeting%20the%20former%20President%20were%20fired%20at%20the%20Butler%20rally%20yesterday.%20Trump%20said%20one%20of%20the%20bullets%20pierced%20the%20upper%20part%20of%20his%20right%20ear.%20One%20person%20was%20killed%20and%20two%20others%20critically%20injured%20in%20the%20shooting.%20Visuals%20showed%20Secret%20Service%20operatives%20escorting%20the%20former%20President%20to%20safety%20after%20the%20shooting%2C%20bloodstains%20on%20his%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20has%20strongly%20condemned%20the%20incident%20and%20also%20spoken%20to%20his%20arch%20rival%20after%20the%20shooting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20place%20in%20America%20for%20this%20kind%20of%20violence.%20It's%20sick.%20It's%20sick.%20It's%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20we%20have%20to%20unite%20this%20country...%20We%20cannot%20be%20like%20this%2C%20we%20cannot%20condone%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20told%20reporters%20in%20an%20emergency%20briefing%20after%20the%20attack%20on%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20that%20there's%20political%20violence%2C%20or%20violence%20in%20America%20like%20this%2C%20is%20just%20unheard%20of.%20It's%20just%20not%20appropriate.%20Everybody%2C%20everybody%20must%20condemn%20it.%20Everybody%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720933740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fbokt02qg_donald-trump-shooting_625x300_14_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-assassination-attempt-donald-trump-shooting-on-identity-and-motive-of-donald-trump-rally-shooter-fbi-gives-an-update-6101826%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Security%20agencies%20in%20the%20US%20are%2