0I%20am%20a%20cricket%20and%20Dhoni%20fan.%20So%2C%20when%20I%20met%20him%2C%20he%20told%20me%20'pata%20hai%20bhai.%20I%20play%20badminton.%20I%20know%20who%20you%20are%20and%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20tell%20me%20that%20you%20are%20Saina's%20husband.'%20He%20spoke%20to%20me%20like%20a%20friend%2C%20as%20if%20I%20am%20his%20teammate%2C%26quot%3B%20Kashyap%20said%20on%20Nikhil%20Tho%20Natakalu's%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFondly%20known%20as%20Thala%2C%20Dhoni%20led%20India%20to%20three%20ICC%20trophies%20and%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20to%20five%20IPL%20titles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhoni%20played%20350%20ODI%20matches%20over%20a%20period%20of%20a%20decade%20and%20a%20half%20and%20accumulated%2010%2C773%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2050.58.%20In%20Test%20cricket%2C%20he%20represented%20India%20in%2090%20matches%20and%20scored%20close%20to%205000%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2038.09.%20In%20the%20IPL%2C%20he%20has%20scored%20over%205000%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20India%20captain%20recently%20celebrated%20his%2043rd%20birthday.%20Having%20announced%20his%20international%20retirement%20in%202020%2C%20Dhoni%20only%20features%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKashyap%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20was%20awarded%20the%20Arjuna%20Award%20by%20the%20Government%20in%202012%20after%20he%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20men's%20badminton%20player%20to%20reach%20the%20quarterfinals%20at%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20won%20the%20gold%20medal%20in%20men's%20singles%20at%20the%202014%20Glasgow%20Commonwealth%20Games.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720924440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fk19fhd1g_parupalli-kashyap-ms-dhoni_625x300_13_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fbadminton%2Fparupalli-kashyap-introduced-himself-as-saina-nehwals-husband-ms-dhonis-response-left-him-stunned-6096702%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian%20badminton%20st