Cli%3EIn%202025%2C%20travelers%20will%20be%20able%20to%20get%20their%20own%20Pan%20Am%20experience%20in%20the%20friendly%20skies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20the%20trip%2C%20which%20begins%20in%20NYC%20and%20will%20feature%20stops%20in%20Bermuda%20and%20across%20Europe%2C%20isn't%20cheap.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20aviation%20fans%20drawn%20to%20the%20Jet%20Age%20of%20the%201950s%20and%201960s%2C%20few%20things%20crystallize%20its%20allure%20more%20than%20Pan%20Am.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20operation%20from%201927%20until%201991%2C%20Pan%20American%20World%20Airways%20symbolized%20the%20ambitions%20of%20a%20rapidly%20developing%20US.%20The%20now-defunct%20airline%20served%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpan-am-photos-show-airline-glory-days-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20pioneer%20in%20the%20evolution%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20commercial%20air%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20next%20year%2C%20travelers%20will%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20experience%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvintage-photos-airplane-flying-2017-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20of%20that%20magic%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPan%20Am%20will%20mark%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.criteriontravel.com%2Fpanam%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eits%20temporary%20return%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20skies%20in%20June%202025%20with%20a%2012-day%20trip%20following%20the%20airline's%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehistoric%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esouthern%20and%20northern%20transatlantic%20routes.%20The%20upcoming%20%26quot%3BTracing%20the%20Transatlantic%26quot%3B%20trip%20is%20backed%20by%20Pan%20American%20World%20Airways%20and%20the%20Pan%20Am%20Museum%20Foundation%2C%20with%20licensing%20by%20Pan%20Am%20Brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2027%2C%202025%2C%20the%20trip%20is%20set%20to%20kick%20off%20in%20New%20York%20City%20on%20a%20Boeing%20757%20airplane%20with%20all-business-class%20seating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor