akes%20the%20wait%20a%20long%20one.%20When%20he%20finally%20does%20reach%20the%20counter%2C%20owner%20Raza%20Hassan%20Saheb%20wastes%20no%20time%20in%20shouting%20out%20orders%20to%20the%20restaurant%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3Esahib%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewaits%20as%20meat%20is%20ground%3B%20slathered%20in%20a%20bowl%20of%20spices%20and%20a%20melange%20of%20onions%2C%20garlic%2C%20ginger%20and%20herbs%3B%20formed%20into%20desired%20shapes%20and%20fitted%20on%20iron%20skewers%20before%20they%20are%20placed%20over%20an%20open%20flame.%20Juicy%2C%20succulent%2C%20delectable%20%E2%80%94%20the%20meats%20give%20off%20an%20enticing%20aroma%20as%20they%20cook%20to%20perfection.%20At%20the%20Nizam%20Restaurant%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F231208%2Findia-unknown-history-kebab-how-recipe-food-tunde-kebabs-nawab-lucknow-wajid-ali%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20making%20of%20%3Cem%3Ekebabs%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20almost%20clockwork%2C%20owing%20to%20the%20burgeoning%20demand%20that%20the%20place%20sees%20from%20British%20officers%20who%20prize%20the%20snack%20for%20the%20amazing%20taste%20it%20delivers%20on%20a%20shoestring%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekebabs%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20ready%2C%20Raza%20suddenly%20has%20an%20idea.%20He%20looks%20around%20for%20a%20spare%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Indian%20flatbread)%20and%20puts%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekebabs%20%3C%2Fem%3Einto%20it%2C%20serving%20the%20%3Cem%3Esahib%3C%2Fem%3E%20his%20much-awaited%20snack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistory%20calls%20this%20moment%20the%20one%20where%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekathi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eroll%20was%20born!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FaJyz8f9XQSo%3Fsi%3DUfZb2ArDb5KspyWv%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInnovation%20at%20its%20best%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fleeting%20inclusion%20(of%20wrapping%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekebab%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20a%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3E)%20was%20an%20ingenious%20one%2C%20and%20soon%2C%20it%20became%20a%20norm%20at%20Nizam%E2%80%99s.%20Raza%20was%20quick%20to%20note%20how%20the%20idea%20put%20a%20smile%20on%20the%20%3Cem%3Esahib%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20face.%20From%20then%20on%2C%20Nizam%E2%80%99s%20decided%20to%20serve%20%E2%80%98that%20dish%E2%80%99%20to%20everyone%20who%20came%20to%20eat%20%3Cem%3Ekebabs%20%3C%2Fem%3Eat%20the%20restaurant.%20The%20fact%20that%20it%20became%20a%20no-mess%20affair%20for%20anyone%20who%20wanted%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F340611%2Fhealthy-snack-brand-startup-open-secret-woman-entrepreneur-ahana-gautam-iit-bombay-harvard%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrab%20a%20quick%20snack%3C%2Fa%3E%20ensured%20its%20longevity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20now%20for%20the%20story%20of%20the%20dish%E2%80%99s%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20hack%20of%20wrapping%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekebab%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20a%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Nizam%E2%80%99s%20also%20decided%20to%20tweak%20its%20strategy%20a%20little.%20The%20iron%20skewers%20that%20were%20in%20use%20were%20proving%20heavy%20and%20tedious%2C%20and%20so%2C%20these%20were%20swapped%20with%20substitutes%20made%20out%20of%20bamboo%20also%20called%20%3Cem%3Ekathi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(the%20Bengali%20word%20for%20stick).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkathi-roll-1720596960.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kathi%20roll%20is%20a%20popular%20snack%20eaten%20around%