20for%20the%20interview%20round.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20interview%20rounds%20for%20both%20CSE%20and%20IFS%20are%20different.%20While%20the%20former%20is%20on%20general%20questions%2C%20the%20latter%20stresses%20on%20technicalities%20of%20the%20forest%20service%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20general%20answers%20might%20suffice%20in%20the%20Civil%20Services%20Examination%20(CSE)%2C%20the%20board%20for%20the%20Indian%20Forest%20Service%20(IFS)%20expects%20scientific%20and%20sustainable%20solutions%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Harsimran%2C%20who%20secured%20210%20marks%20out%20of%20300%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F347452%2Fupsc-cse-samyak-jain-visually-impaired-assistant-collector-puducherry-topper-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epersonality%20test%20round%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20preparing%20for%20the%20interview%2C%20I%20covered%20basic%20questions%20about%20my%20background%2C%20job%20experience%2C%20degrees%2C%20hobbies%2C%20and%20interests.%20Additionally%2C%20I%20focused%20on%20technical%20aspects%20related%20to%20forestry%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20during%20the%20interview%20round%2C%20he%20was%20asked%20about%20various%20types%20of%20forest%20fires%20and%20strategies%20to%20improve%20groundwater%20quality%20affected%20by%20the%20overuse%20of%20chemical%20fertilisers%20in%20farms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Harsimran%20Singh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720620910000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-1-1720617346.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D356313%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20initial%20setbacks%20in%20UPSC%20CSE%20attempts%2C%20Harsimran%20Singh%20Cheema%20persisted%2C%20achieving%20an%20All%20India%20R