0true%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20scientific%20aspect%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrish%20Ashok%20embarked%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20unravel%20this%20science%20and%20share%20it%20with%20the%20world.%20When%20he%20moved%20to%20the%20US%20for%20work%2C%20he%20discovered%20that%20his%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20potato%20fry%20far%20outshone%20his%20own.%20How%20does%20one%20achieve%20that%20elusive%20perfect%20crispness%3F%20Why%20do%20you%20add%20some%20spices%20after%20others%20and%20roast%20them%20for%20lesser%20times%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20because%20the%20recipe%20book%20says%20so.%20It%E2%80%99s%20due%20to%20chemical%20reactions%20that%20occur.%20The%20search%20behind%20these%20reasons%20led%20to%20Ashok%E2%80%99s%20journey%20towards%20becoming%20a%20kitchen%20alchemist!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20780px)%20100vw%2C%20780px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkrish-ashok-1720529628.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22780%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ashok%20with%20his%20parents%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkrish-ashok-1720529628.jpg%20780w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkrish-ashok-1720529628-300x197.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkrish-ashok-1720529628-500x328.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkrish-ashok-1720529628-768x504.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkrish-ashok-1720529628-150x98.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356120%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAshok%20with%20his%20parents%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20head%20for%20AI%20Cloud%20Advisory%20and%20Consulting%20at%20TCS%20(Tata%20Consultancy%20Services)%2C%20Ashok%20applies%20his%20training%20as%20an%20engineer%20to%20decode%20the%20science%20behind%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353745%2Fakash-muralidharan-masterchef-tamil-winner-vizha-medai-south-indian-food-adhd-ravioli-rasam-pongal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20cooking%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Starting%20with%20a%20humour%20blog%20in%20the%20nineties%2C%20he%20wrote%20a%20book%20called%20%E2%80%98Masala%20Lab%E2%80%99%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfterwards%2C%20his%20journey%20on%20social%20media%20began%2C%20sharing%20intriguing%20tidbits%20from%20his%20book.%20He%20eventually%20took%20on%20prevalent%20scaremongering%20about%20certain%20ingredients%20and%20foods%20that%20are%20said%20to%20harm%20health.%20The%2046-year-old%20started%20myth-busting%20and%20explaining%20straightforward%20concepts%2C%20such%20as%20why%20it%E2%80%99s%20perfectly%20fine%20to%20use%20a%20microwave%20oven%20or%20air%20fryer%2C%20why%20storing%20food%20in%20the%20fridge%20is%20safe%2C%20and%20why%20variations%20in%20salt%20types%20don%E2%80%99t%20significantly%20impact%20your%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20characteristic%20wit%20and%20sass%20won%20over%20the%20internet%2C%20offering%20a%20dose%20of%20sanity%20and%20science%20in%20a%20space%20crowded%20by%20people%20looking%20for%20two-minute%20fame%20without%20substantiating%20their%20claims%20with%20facts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChemical%20engineering%20in%20a%20home%20lab%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20a%20progressive%20household%20in%20Chennai%2C%20Krish%20Ashok%20was%20encouraged%20by%20his%20father%20to%20experiment%20with%20various%20kinds%20of%20food%20outside%20the%20home.%20He%20began%20cooking%20as%20a%20teenager%2C%20but%20his%20real%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F299901%2Fnri-chef-vijaya-kumar-semma-new-york-city-michelin-star-south-indian-restaurant%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejourney%20with%20cooking%3C%2Fa%3E%20started%20when%20he%20moved%20to%20the%20US%20for%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FFi-1-1720529288.gif%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Myth%20busting%20with%20Krish%20Ashok%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356117%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20moving%2C%20he%20meticulously%20wrote%20down%20recipes%20from%20his%20mother%2C%20grandmother%2C%20and%20other%20older%20women%20in%20the%20family.%20He%20found%20their%20way%20of%20sharing%20recipes%20fascinatingly%20different%20from%20cookbook%20methods.%20Their%20inherent%20knowledge%20of%20the%20science%20of%20cooking%2C%20without%20viewing%20it%20through%20a%20scientist%E2%80%99s%20or%20engineer%E2%80%99s%20lens%2C%20captivated%20Ashok%20and%20sparked%20his%20interest%20in%20food%20science.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20original%20interest%20in%20food%20science%20happened%20when%20I%20recognised%20that%20the%20way%20my%20grandmother%20or%20grand-aunt%20thought%20about%20food%20was%20fundamentally%20different%20from%20how%20recipe%20books%20tended%20to%20think%20about%20it.%20It%20was%20evident%20that%20my%20grandmother%20was%20thinking%20about%20food%20as%20heuristics%20and%20algorithms%20and%20in%20a%20very%20scientific%20way%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ashok%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20when%20he%20referred%20to%20cookbooks%2C%20they%20missed%20out%20on%20this%20important%20tacit%20knowledge.%20%E2%80%9CCookbooks%20don%E2%80%99t%20tell%20you%20why%20you%20need%20to%20add%20two%20cups%20of%20water%20for%20rice.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20teach%20you%20how%20to%20adjust%20for%20more%20rice%20or%20how%20to%20find%20out%20if%20something%20is%20cooked.%20Whe