%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351707%2Fdoon-gooseberry-farm-dehradun-sisters-amla-farming-growing-mangoes-brinjals-tomatoes-lemons-in-hilly-areas%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epowders%20and%20masalas%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20over%20500%20families%20and%20are%20present%20in%2025%20organic%20shops%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20besides%20being%20available%20online.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20even%20opened%20their%20own%20shop%20in%20Coimbatore%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20now%20sell%20over%20120%20kg%20of%20products%20every%20month%2C%20which%20makes%20them%20over%20Rs%2060%2C000%20monthly.%20Their%20powders%20today%20include%20sambhar%2C%20rasam%2C%20different%20spinach%20(keerai)%20powders%2C%20%3Cem%3Eidli%20podi%3C%2Fem%3E%20masalas%20like%20biryani%2C%20chicken%2C%20mutton%20and%20soup%20powders.%20Their%20bestsellers%20are%20the%20soup%20powders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20hopes%20that%20more%20women%20come%20forward%20to%20start%20their%20own%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20this%20from%20our%20rented%20house%20with%20just%20Rs%202%2C000.%20You%20need%20to%20believe%20in%20yourself.%20There%20are%20many%20avenues%20to%20educate%20yourself%20and%20expand%20your%20horizons.%20The%20sky%E2%80%99s%20the%20limit%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20can%20buy%20the%20products%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finiyaorganics.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20images%20courtesy%3A%20Sudha%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720448911000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsudhaa-min-1720445265.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D355942%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Once%20a%20teach