o%20what%20fuels%20his%20drive%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%20lies%20in%20the%20way%20Tiwari%E2%80%99s%20eyes%20light%20up%20each%20monsoon%20as%20the%20rains%20grace%20his%20village%2C%20filling%20up%20the%20rural%20ponds%20that%20had%20lain%20barren%20for%20years.%20Watching%20them%20spring%20to%20life%20is%20all%20the%20validation%20he%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20achieving%20the%20feat%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20easy%2C%20he%20shares%2C%20adding%20that%20sometimes%20the%20stubborn%20climate%20posed%20hurdles%C2%A0%20%E2%80%94%20relentless%20heat%20waves%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20with%20temperatures%20touching%2045%20degrees%20Celsius%20would%20cause%20the%20water%20bodies%20to%20run%20dry%20%E2%80%94%20while%20other%20times%2C%20it%20was%20his%20friends%20and%20family%20who%20were%20against%20his%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Tiwari%20has%20remained%20unfazed.%20And%20his%20stoicism%20was%20eventually%20met%20with%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20chat%20with%20him%2C%20we%20explore%20how%20this%20PhD%20student%E2%80%99s%20model%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296139%2Ftamil-nadu-man-quits-dubai-job-to-revive-water-bodies-help-lakhs-after-cyclone-india-water-warriors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereviving%20water%20bodies%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20well%20be%20a%20gold%20standard%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20rural%20landscape%20that%20is%20struggling%20with%20water%20problems%20in%20the%20face%20of%20changing%20climate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAs%20precious%20as%20gold%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20nursery%20rhymes%20we%20grew%20up%20hearing%20are%20rooted%20in%20our%20memories.%20Likewise%20for%20Tiwari%20and%20the%20children%20of%20his%20village%3B%20albeit%20the%20rhymes%20were%20slightly%20different.%20Veering%20away%20from%20the%20popular%20ones%2C%20these%20verses%20emphasised%20the%20crucial%20importance%20of%20water%20in%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDhaura%20tera%20paanee%20gajab%20kari%20jae%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3Egagaree%20(matakee)%20na%20phootai%2C%20khasam%20(pati)%20maree%20jae.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETranslating%20these%20lines%2C%20and%20underscoring%20their%20meaning%2C%20Tiwari%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20%5Bthe%20rhyme%5D%20originated%20centuries%20ago%20when%20the%20women%20of%20the%20village%20would%20walk%20for%20miles%20to%20fetch%20water%20from%20a%20certain%20pond.%20The%20water%20was%20considered%20so%20prized%20and%20expensive%20that%20the%20women%20would%20often%20pray%20to%20God%20to%20not%20let%20the%20%3Cem%3Ematkas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(mud%20pots)%20crack%20and%20tell%20Him%20that%20He%20could%20take%20away%20their%20husbands%20instead.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rhyme%2C%20though%20morbid%2C%20encapsulates%20the%20pedestal%20on%20which%20water%20was%20put%20in%20the%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages--1720083198.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rambabu%20Tiwari's%20pond%20revival%20projects%20are%20targeted%20at%20mobilising%20community%20efforts.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages--1720083198.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages--1720083198-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages--1720083198-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages--1720083198-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages--1720083198-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355528%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERambabu%20Tiwari%E2%80%99s%20pond%20revival%20projects%20are%20targeted%20at%20mobilising%20community%20efforts%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Tiwari%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETiwari%E2%80%99s%20earliest%20memories%20involve%20being%20scolded%20for%20accidentally%20breaking%20a%20pot%20or%20two%20while%20playing%20around%20the%20house%20with%20his%20friends.%20%E2%80%9CEach%20drop%20was%20considered%20to%20be%20gold%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20owes%20to%20the%20complex%20relationship%20that%20Bundelkhand%20has%20had%20with%20water.%20The%20region%20%E2%80%94%20which%20was%20once%20interspersed%20with%20thick%20forests%20%E2%80%94%20is%20now%20characteristic%20of%20bare%2C%20hilly%20terrain.%20And%20as%20a%20report%20by%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Disaster%20Management%20(2014)%20suggests%2C%20the%20droughts%20are%20to%20blame%20for%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20concluded%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332290%2Fmaharashtra-water-scarcity-drought-prone-jalna-district-gets-aid-water-bodies-desilted%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esevere%20drought%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20sharply%20increased%20in%20the%20last%2030%20years%20in%20Bundelkhand.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20records%20from%20the%20Government%20show%20a%20spell%20of%20one%20drought%20in%2016%20years%20during%20the%2018th%20and%2019th%20centuries%20in%20Bundelkhand.%20From%201968%20to%201992%2C%20the%20region%20saw%20a%20drought%20every%20five%20years.%20However%20in%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20the%20region%20has%20already%20suffered%20seven%20years%20of%20drought%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20light%20of%20this%2C%20conserving%20water%20was%20second%20nature%20for%20Tiwari.%20But%20these%20ideals%20tended%20to%20get%20blurred%20when%20he%20moved%20to%20Allahabad%20for%20further%20studies%20in%202012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bathroom%20of%20his%20own%3B%20showers%20for%20baths%3B%20unlimited%20water%20supply%20and%20no%20one%20having%20to%20walk%20miles%20to%20fetch%20it%2C%20introduced%20Tiwari%20to%20a%20whole%20new%20world.%20He%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20believe%20his%20luck.%20But%20while%20the%20initial%20weeks%20of%20this%20%E2%80%9Cfantasy%20life%E2%80%9D%20pushed%20all%20thoughts%20of%20water%20scarcity%20out%20of%20his%20mind%2C%20weekend%20visits%20back%20home%20did%20not%20allow%20him%20to%20forget%20about%20his%20village%E2%80%99s%20woes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20began%20to%20draw%20parallels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-1-1720083334.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Bajrang%20Sagar%20pond%20that%20Rambabu%20Tiwari%20has%20helped%20revive%20was%20previously%20barren%20and%20filled%20with%20silt%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-1-1720083334.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-1-1720083334-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-1-1720083334-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-1-1720083334-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpond-revival-in-villages-1-1720083334-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-355530%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Bajrang%20Sagar%20pond%20that%20Rambabu%20Tiwari%20has%20helped%